<paragraph blockId="0.[1210,2099,611,1230]" pageId="0" pageNumber="288">• Deserts, steppes, urban grasslands, forests, farmlands, alpine meadows, parks, and gardens (hedgehogs) or humid, tropical forests (gymnures).</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1210,2099,611,1230]" box="[1211,1703,1119,1152]" pageId="0" pageNumber="288">• 10 genera, 26 species, 4b taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1210,2099,611,1230]" pageId="0" pageNumber="288">• 2 species Endangered, 1 species Vulnerable; none Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
